    {
      "id": "intro-0",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "简介",
      "body": "[Erlang](https://www.erlang.org/) 是一种用于构建并发、分布式和容错系统的编程语言。以下是一些常用的命令和操作。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-1",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "启动 Erlang Shell",
      "body": "```shell\nerl\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-2",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "编译代码",
      "body": "```shell\n# 在 Erlang Shell 中编译\nc(module).\n# 在命令行中编译\nerlc module.erl\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-3",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "运行代码",
      "body": "```shell\n# 在 Erlang Shell 中运行\nmodule:function().\n# 从命令行运行\nerl -noshell -s module function -s init stop\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-4",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "退出 Erlang Shell",
      "body": "```shell\nq().\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-5",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "模块定义",
      "body": "```erlang\n-module(module_name).\n-export([function_name/arity, ...]).\n\nfunction_name(Args) ->\n    % Function body.\n    Result.\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-6",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "导出函数",
      "body": "```erlang\n-export([function1/0, function2/1]).\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-7",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "注释",
      "body": "```erlang\n% 单行注释\n% 这是一个注释\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-8",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F",
      "body": "%60%60%60erlang%0AVarName%20%3D%20Value.%20%25%20%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E5%90%8D%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%86%99%E5%AD%97%E6%AF%8D%E5%BC%80%E5%A4%B4%0AAge%20%3D%2025.%0AName%20%3D%20%22Alice%22.%0A%60%60%60",
