      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "条件语句",
      "body": "```erlang\nif\n    Condition1 -> Expression1;\n    Condition2 -> Expression2;\n    true -> DefaultExpression\nend.\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-17",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "case 表达式",
      "body": "```erlang\ncase Expression of\n    Pattern1 -> Expression1;\n    Pattern2 -> Expression2;\n    _ -> DefaultExpression\nend.\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-18",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "函数定义",
      "body": "```erlang\n% 无参函数\nmy_function() ->\n    ok.\n\n% 有参函数\nadd(A, B) ->\n    A + B.\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-19",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "列表生成",
      "body": "```erlang\n% 生成 1 到 10 的列表\n[ X || X <- lists:seq(1, 10)].\n\n% 生成 1 到 10 中的偶数\n[ X || X <- lists:seq(1, 10), X rem 2 == 0].\n```"
    },
